body_html:
The Windows cmake test failed because of a checkout issue. The Linux CPU test failed the api compatibility test. That passes here with (albeit with this PR on top of master), with:

bazel test --verbose_failures --config=cuda --config=opt //tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test

I'll see if it was broken on master when I made the PR, but I'm away for a few days now.
